Package au.edu.anu.twcore.ecosystem.runtime

Interface DynamicSystem

All Known Subinterfaces:
CategorizedComponent
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArenaComponent, GroupComponent, HierarchicalComponent, LifeCycleComponent, SystemComponent
public interface DynamicSystem
Objects that have state variables that can be modified along time should implement this interface.

3Worlds: component threeWorlds

Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 27 sept. 2012 updated 20/2/2017
